{
  "stem": "22586.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] And later on, they took these bodies and piled them up high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] And they were just left there in a pile, because they had no time to bury them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to take care of first other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, our heads were shaven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were given this gray dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were taken back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And every morning, about 4 o'clock, we went out to what was called a Zahlappell, they counted us, lined up and they counted us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stood there for several hours until somebody came and went through the whole camp counting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we would go back into our barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were not assigned any work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I remember I volunteered to go and pick up the coffee or bread, whatever there was, to another camp, because I always thought that maybe-- [CRYING] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe I'll see my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, I never did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was-- I really didn't do anything in Auschwitz except standing in Zahlappell, morning and at night again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were in Auschwitz for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, during one of the Zahlappells, they picked out-- during these Zahlappells, they used to pick out people who were not-- who got sick.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were always picked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, after the six weeks, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they told us that we'll be taken out of Auschwitz to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they took us to-- back to a train again, to-- and we went to Gelsenkirchen, Gelsenberg in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And there, as we arrived, we were put into some kind of a big tent building.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
